## CRITICAL FINDING: Tournament Economy
Downloaded tournament match logs (v65 vs v364, 4a each).
- `num_agents=8` in tournament (total env), each player controls 4
- With 4 agents: 3 aligners + 1 miner → silicon depletes to 5 by step 1500!
- Economy collapse → only 1 aligner, Clips takes over

## TV15 Design (Tournament Economy Fix)
- Detect tournament: `team_size < num_agents`
- Cap at 2 aligners for 4-agent sub-team (ensures 2 miners)
- Silicon priority mining only in tournament mode (when < 100)
- TV12 stagnation exploration base
- TV9 2-agent fix

